Subject: When selecting to display duplicate computers the page keeps loading till it times out
Description: When selecting to display duplicate computers the page keeps loading till it times out
What_We_Know__c:
We searched for a computer on the customers side and it appeared as a duplicate(2 items, all the fields identical except for last seen where there was a difference of 20-30 minutes). The computer appeared as Licensed and Offline.

Issue:
In the Device Computer -> Computers -> Filter menu: if we select in the Duplicates field "Yes" and apply, the page will keep loading till it times out.
I tried replicating this issue on my end(but I do not have duplicate computers) and it loaded instantly returning 0 computers.
Next_Steps__c:
05Feb: Customer is migrating the EPP server to our hosted environment in AWS. Once it is completed I will check again with the customer regarding the duplicate computer search issue.
Waiting on R&D to provide clarification / details on one of the instructions.
Solution_Comment__c: After migration the issue is no longer present.
